OL,3,CBuilding firm works to save lives as
OL,4,Cindustry faces 'mental health
OL,5,Cemergency'
OL,7,FThe construction industry is facing a
OL,8,Fmental health emergency, with rates of
OL,9,Fdeath by suicide more than three times
OL,10,Fthe national average.
OL,12,F7,000 workers in the UK have died over
OL,13,Fthe past decade; last year alone, 355
OL,14,Fskilled tradespeople took their own
OL,15,Flives.
OL,17,FOne company in Oxfordshire says it's
OL,18,Fworking hard to change attitudes and
OL,19,Fsave lives, and has recently won a
OL,20,Fnational award for making a difference.
