OL,3,CBuilding firm works to save lives as
OL,4,Cindustry faces 'mental health
OL,5,Cemergency'
OL,7,F"We have a directly-employed workforce
OL,8,Fand a sub-contract pool that we call
OL,9,Fupon, it's a very male-led environment
OL,10,Fand a very non-speaking environment in
OL,11,Fthat sector, in terms of mental health.
OL,13,F"So we invested in our team to become
OL,14,Fmental health ambassadors."
OL,16,FThe company has trained up mental
OL,17,Fhealth champions, including Fred
OL,18,FKirkness, who says he loves the
OL,19,Findustry and the people he meets.
