OL,3,CBuilding firm works to save lives as
OL,4,Cindustry faces 'mental health
OL,5,Cemergency'
OL,7,F"We're not doctors by any stretch, but
OL,8,Fwe're trained on the key things to
OL,9,Fnotice, has someone's mood changed
OL,10,Fslightly or maybe they're
OL,11,Ftimekeeping's gone off.
OL,13,F"We work closely with a charity called
OL,14,Fthe Lighthouse Charity, and they have
OL,15,Floads of resources available to
OL,16,Fsupport people who need some support
OL,17,Fduring what can be some tough times on
OL,18,Fa building site."
