OL,3,CBuilding firm works to save lives as
OL,4,Cindustry faces 'mental health
OL,5,Cemergency'
OL,7,FThe company, which is based in Thame
OL,8,Fbut works across Oxfordshire,
OL,9,FBuckinghamshire, Hampshire and the
OL,10,FCotswolds, has recently won a national
OL,11,Frecognition for setting a benchmark
OL,12,Ffor culture and mental health
OL,13,Fprovision, winning a Federation of
OL,14,FMaster Builders award.
OL,16,FWorkers are currently turning a 19th-
OL,17,Fcentury former church in Oxford, which
OL,18,Fwas converted into a cafe and meeting
OL,19,Fspace, back into a church, one of only
OL,20,Ftwo such projects in the UK.
